body:
execution/protectors.h: protector declarations for NoUndetectableObjects

Excerpt:
#define DECLARED_PROTECTORS_ON_ISOLATE(V)                                     \
  ...
  V(NoUndetectableObjects, NoUndetectableObjectsProtector,                    \
    no_undetectable_objects_protector)

And the DECLARE_PROTECTOR_ON_ISOLATE macro expands to:
  V8_EXPORT_PRIVATE static inline bool IsNoUndetectableObjectsIntact(Isolate* isolate);
  V8_EXPORT_PRIVATE static void InvalidateNoUndetectableObjects(Isolate* isolate);
explanation: Header defines protector name and helper APIs IsNoUndetectableObjectsIntact and InvalidateNoUndetectableObjects. This entry maps to protectors.h lines.
